deck: Paris was an androgynous android
description: Paris was an androgynous android originally created in France to demonstrate advances in robotics by playing chess with humans. Paris was later modified by a criminal named Melton to commit crimes. Originally, Paris moved with a stiff gate and squeaked when it was low on grease. Melton modified it, giving him great strength and agility, in addition to its superior mathematical timing and highly strategic tactics. It was capable of juggling, walking a tight rope, swinging on a trapeeze, and lifting a full grown man over its head. It could also drive and pick locks. However, Paris was unable to speak, felt no pain, and had no moral reasoning. It was built with more than half a million dollar worth of diamonds, which helped it to function. It was eventually stopped by Boy King and his Giant, after it killed Melton by throwing him from the high wire at a circus.
name: Paris

deck: Former physics professor who later worked for the Russian mob as money launderer.
description:
Origin

Isaac Kessler was a former physics professor forced to reign his tenure in disgrace after falsifying experimental results. Eventually, he found himself working for Dimitri Solokov's mob, where he displayed an uncanny skill for money laundering.

Major Story Arcs

Kessler was Dimitri's favorite "son" until he started making the profits disappear, as well. He engineered years of such embezzlement, all the while undetected. By the time Solokov caught on, Kessler had managed to spirit away over 200 million dollars of his boss' illicit lucre. Just before the hammer came down, he killed himself.

Not believing him to be dead, Solokov hired John Tower to investigate Kessler's death. Tower discovered Kessler had bought a decommisioned military warehouse. Breaking in, he walked into Kessler, who somehow had managed to retain his memories after dying. Now a living ghost, Kessler tried to flee from Tower, but was killed by Tower using his phasma-knife.

His history is mysterious, but what little we have learned has taught us that he comes from a alternate reality or another world that has perished, and that he turned himself into sound to break through the barrier to reach our planet. Once he got into our world he then possessed a spacesuit that was in some lone quacks home, to start his reign of terror.
